<dl id="n40037a"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n40" href="#n40037a">N40 (VI.B.28B)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n40all.htm#n40037a"> 37(a)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> infant standard</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Teaching is very uphill work, for three chief reasons, namely, there are insufficient books and slates; he is the only teacher for three classes (the undisciplined urchins in the infant standard really require his undivided attention); attendance is irregular. <small> Rev W.S. Hunt, <a name="WSHI1" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#WSHI1"><cite title="source">India's Outcastes: A New Era</cite></a> (1924) 77</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
